Jack Jezzro - Christmas Guitar 320cbr (Big Papi) 2009 Easy Listening Instrumental Electric Guitar

Now this is a very nice and smooth electric guitar collection of favorite Christmas tunes. Big Papi like.... - Big Papi
-

By Digital Dealer
There is so much Piano, Violin and other Instrumentals of Christmas Music. It is great to find a new and elegant sound like Jezzro's electric guitar. You seldom here this beautiful solo sound on a jazz album. It is wonderful music for dinners, trimming the tree or opening presents. It will fill your house with the sounds of christmas and you will find that you can listen to it for hours.
